name: RomanianIdNumberTest
description: Test suite for validating Romanian ID number generation and related functionalities.

test_cases.name: sample
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a valid Romanian ID number and verifies it matches a 13-digit pattern.

test_cases.name: firstDigit_18xx
test_cases.description: Tests the first digit generation for years between 1800 and 1899, verifying male and female specific digits.

test_cases.name: firstDigit_19xx
test_cases.description: Tests the first digit generation for years between 1900 and 1999, verifying male and female specific digits.

test_cases.name: firstDigit_20xx
test_cases.description: Tests the first digit generation for years between 2000 and 2099, verifying male and female specific digits.

test_cases.name: dateOfBirth
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of a LocalDate to a date of birth string in the format used for Romanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: countyCode
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of county codes and verifies they match a 2-digit pattern and are within the expected range.

test_cases.name: sequenceNumber
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a sequence number and verifies it matches a 3-digit pattern.

test_cases.name: checksum
test_cases.description: Tests the checksum calculation for a given Romanian ID number string.
